Just working on connectivity tonight. My BSP decided to stop communicating through USB. Had the idea to send midi to the iPad using the mono station midi thru. Midi thru doesn't go through USB on the mono station. ☹️ Oh well, still synced it all and had the Microbrute clocking the pocket operator. Fun fun nonsensical noise!

What sick twisted sort of animal would have done this?

#dolphinfreetuna

This little piece of gear has totally changed my opinion of electronic music and the instruments used to make it. I just started playing around with electronic music about a year ago. Prior to that I played bass guitar almost exclusively and thought electronic music was just a bunch of knob twisting and button pushing. It wasn't really making music, the instruments were. The @wearenovation Mono Station is a beast. I'm just starting to scratch the surface of it's capabilities. I've played it along side my MiniNova and mind blown. If you haven't played one you need to.

Ever have gear show up too early?
I was trying to get my desk setup before my new #arturia_official #microfreak showed up. I just ordered it from #sweetwater yesterday!! I wasn't expecting to see it until Friday. Very difficult to refrain from opening it up and playing  instead of finishing my desk. Great job with another #newgearday !

Now to, BRING THE NOISE!! #synth #synthesizer #electric_locust #electricmusic #arturia #ipadmusic #irig #caustic #beatsteppro #behringer #behringerneutron #korgvolca #korg #akai

I'm not really much for astrology however a lot of things have seem to be falling into place lately. While setting up a new set up in my office I just happened to grab cans out of the pantry that are the exact same height as my volca keys? It also happened to be the only 4 same sized cans in there. I could go on and on. 
Enjoy your weekend
